Author: ShannonAnon
Text: I wish. I gained 5 pounds in one week thanks to Thanksgiving. I was 1.5 pounds away from my goal...

Author: jaksusu
Text: Me me me!!  I think something to do with the fact that I know there’s always big meals around the corner that I have no control over (whereas you don’t really get that so much in summer or whatever) so I’m in a constant state of anxiety.    Add to that a touch of what I suspect could be SAD for a lot of us (*me*) idk but I’m always skinnier in the winter
